	<text>
		<body>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Philada</placeName> <date>Octr 3 1850</date></p>
				<p>My Dear Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Three hundred copies of the<lb/> &#8220;Geography of <placeName>Palestine</placeName>&#8221; having been disposed<lb/> of to this date. I send <sic>inclosed</sic> Forty&#45;five<lb/> Dollars for your copyright on that no. of<lb/> copies. I also beg your acceptance of the<lb/> offering &#40;&#36;25&#41; made to you in the Synagogue<lb/> on the <date>1st day of &#8220;Roshashana&#8221;</date> &#38; which I should<lb/> have sent before Had I not been absent<lb/> from the City immediately thereafter &#38; on my<lb/> return it escaped my memory till this moment.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Trusting that your health is reinstated<lb/> and that you may hereafter enjoy that<lb/> first of blessings together with all the<lb/> happiness this life affords&#44; is the sincere<lb/> wish of &#160;&#160;&#160;Your friend</p>
			<p rend="indent(11)"><persName role="author">A Hart</persName></p>
				<p>To the <addressee>Rev I Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>371 Walnut St</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">&#40;Ck enclosed on the Philad Bank for &#36;70&#41;</p>
		</body>
